      <title>中国大型CEO峰会笼罩在政策和准入疑虑之中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/china-s-big-ceo-summit-clouded-by-doubts-over-policy-access</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国在本周末于北京举行的年度论坛上吸引全球高层管理人员的努力已经因他们将与哪些高层领导人会面的猜测而蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/china-s-big-ceo-summit-clouded-by-doubts-over-policy-access</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前外交官称特朗普的批评是陆克文的“荣誉勋章”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/trump-criticism-is-a-badge-of-honor-for-rudd-ex-diplomat-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚前外交官杰夫·芮捷锐 (Geoff Raby) 周五对彭博电视台表示，澳大利亚驻美国大使陆克文将佩戴前总统唐纳德·特朗普对他的批评作为“荣誉徽章”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/trump-criticism-is-a-badge-of-honor-for-rudd-ex-diplomat-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 02:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内政大臣誓言通过更新尖峰法来追究肇事者的责任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-22/home-secretary-vows-to-hold-perpetrators-to-account-by-updating-law-on-spiking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[内政大臣发誓要严厉打击飙升行为，他表示，肇事者将通过法律的修改“被追究责任”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-22/home-secretary-vows-to-hold-perpetrators-to-account-by-updating-law-on-spiking</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 00:02:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国援助停滞，国际货币基金组织批准向乌克兰提供 8.8 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/imf-approves-880-million-for-ukraine-with-us-assistance-stalled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织 (IMF) 已批准向乌克兰提供下一笔 156 亿美元贷款计划，此举将提振该国的财政，因为其主要盟友美国的援助仍处于停滞状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/imf-approves-880-million-for-ukraine-with-us-assistance-stalled</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 22:55:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被起诉的参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯调侃独立竞选连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/senator-menendez-says-he-hopes-for-reelection-as-independent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州参议员罗伯特·梅嫩德斯周四表示，如果联邦腐败指控被证明无罪，他希望以“独立民主党人”的身份寻求连任，但排除了参加民主党初选的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/senator-menendez-says-he-hopes-for-reelection-as-independent</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 22:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥将为委内瑞拉人提供就业机会并提供 660 美元回国津贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/mexico-to-offer-venezuelans-jobs-660-stipend-to-return-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥表示，将向同意返回家园的委内瑞拉人提供就业机会和 660 美元的津贴，作为减少移民的共同努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/mexico-to-offer-venezuelans-jobs-660-stipend-to-return-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 21:43:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
